      <title>印度家庭预计未来几个月通胀将加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/indian-households-see-inflation-accelerating-in-next-few-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行的一项调查显示，印度家庭预计未来三个月至一年内通胀将加速，主要受食品和住房价格的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/indian-households-see-inflation-accelerating-in-next-few-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
