    <item>
      <title>埃里安称，这份就业报告将为 7 月降息画上句号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/this-jobs-report-close-door-on-july-cut-el-erian-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[剑桥大学皇后学院院长穆罕默德·埃利安表示，5 月份就业报告“关闭了”美联储降息的大门。他在“彭博监测”节目中发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/this-jobs-report-close-door-on-july-cut-el-erian-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的罗森伯格质疑美联储的限制性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/blackrock-s-rosenberg-questions-restrictiveness-of-fed-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德系统性多策略基金投资组合经理杰弗里·罗森伯格表示，在 5 月份美国就业报告公布后，美联储的货币政策可能没有想象中那么紧缩。他在彭博电视台发表讲话。非农就业人数超过预期，达到 272,000 人，而失业率意外上升至 4%，为两年多以来的首次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/blackrock-s-rosenberg-questions-restrictiveness-of-fed-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BTG 即将宣布收购纽约银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/btg-is-said-to-be-close-to-announcing-new-york-bank-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，拉美最大的独立投资银行 Banco BTG Pactual SA 即将宣布收购纽约的一家财富管理银行，作为其全球扩张战略的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/btg-is-said-to-be-close-to-announcing-new-york-bank-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:13:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据令美联储降息预期减弱，美国国债收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/treasuries-yields-surge-as-hot-jobs-data-dim-fed-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场意外走强，迫使交易员减少对美联储今年降息的押注，美国国债收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/treasuries-yields-surge-as-hot-jobs-data-dim-fed-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:39:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利法院维持对 ION 子公司股息融资的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/italian-restriction-on-how-ion-raises-debt-for-dividends-upheld-by-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利一家法院支持政府的一项决定，限制 ION 集团旗下子公司如何使用债券销售收益，可能禁止其通过举债向母公司支付股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/italian-restriction-on-how-ion-raises-debt-for-dividends-upheld-by-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TDR Capital 收购亿万富翁 Zuber Issa 持有的 Asda 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/tdr-capital-buys-billionaire-zuber-issa-s-stake-in-asda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TDR Capital 收购了加油站亿万富翁 Zuber Issa 在 Asda 的股份，使该私募股权公司获得了英国最大连锁超市之一的多数控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/tdr-capital-buys-billionaire-zuber-issa-s-stake-in-asda</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 10:34:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据打击美联储降息希望，中国暂停购买黄金，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国一份重要就业报告意外强劲，粉碎了人们对美联储将很快开始降低借贷成本的希望，金价出现四月份以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:06:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
